5. ETHICAL USE RESTRICTIONS (MANDATORY - SEE ETHICAL_USE_POLICY.md)

   The use of this Software is STRICTLY PROHIBITED for:
   
   a) GENETIC USE RESTRICTION TECHNOLOGIES (GURTs): Any breeding activity
      involving the development, research, testing, or commercialization of
      plant varieties incorporating technologies that render seeds sterile,
      non-viable, or dependent on proprietary chemical inducers.
   
   b) TERMINATOR TECHNOLOGY: Any technology that produces sterile seeds,
      preventing farmers from saving and replanting seeds from their harvest.
   
   c) TRAITOR TECHNOLOGY: Any technology requiring chemical application to
      activate or maintain specific genetic traits in plants.
   
   d) SEED TERMINATION TECHNOLOGY: Any method that prevents seeds from being
      saved, replanted, or used for subsequent generations of cultivation.
   
   e) Any activity that directly or indirectly supports, enables, or
      contributes to the creation or deployment of the above technologies.
   
   This prohibition is ABSOLUTE and admits NO EXCEPTIONS. Violation results
   in immediate and automatic termination of all license rights.
   
   For complete terms, see ETHICAL_USE_POLICY.md which is incorporated herein
   by reference and has the same legal force as this license.

